            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> deabus Quadruvis <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> dis deabusque <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sereni</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> At<lb break="no" n="4"/>ticus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> pro <lb n="5"/>sua et suorum salute <lb n="6"/>posuit IIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ian</abbr><ex>uarias</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Agricola et Clem<lb break="no" n="8"/>entino co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Relief mit Darstellung der Vierwegegöttinnen. Links und rechts des Reliefs jeweils übereinander die Buchstaben IH und DD.</p>
            </div>
